      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": true,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Information",
        "text": "<h2>Product Information</h2><ul><li>Powered by Hypochlorous Acid and enriched with Chamomile</li><li>Safe for face, body, and surfaces</li><li>Hypoallergenic and suitable for sensitive skin</li><li>Clinically proven to reduce bacteria and inflammation</li><li>Non-drying and leaves no residue</li><li>Light, natural HOCl scent that dissipates quickly</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_werVVb": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Usage Instructions",
        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p><strong>How To Use:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Post-workout essential:</strong> Spray right after a gym session to help keep breakouts at bay before you can get to a full cleanse.</li><li><strong>Post-workout essential:</strong> In between washes, a spray on your pillowcase can help keep breakout-causing germs under control.</li><li><strong>Pre-treatments purifier:</strong> Before Micro-Infusion, give your skin a spritz to cleanse and prep for better results.</li><li><strong>Device defender:</strong> After using your Q-Rejuvalight Pro, a light spray and wipe inside your device keeps it clean.</li></ol>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_p7UQPA": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Reduces impurities and prevents breakouts without stripping or drying out the skin.</li><li>Accelerates skin healing post-treatment or during flare-ups.</li><li>Use on-the-go to keep skin calm and clear - no rising needed.</li><li>Dermatologically tested, versatile and safe for use on your face, body, and devices.</li><li>Safe for sensitive skin and gentle enough for daily use.</li><li>Travel-friendly breakout control, available in two sizes.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_TwxkfN": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_jzqpe6": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p>Remember to <strong>add a personal touch</strong> to the messaging, talk about how it makes your skin feel and when you use it.</p><p>Examples:</p><ul><li>“My skin flares up after the gym, and this calms it down instantly.”</li><li>“I always keep this in my bag to use when I'm traveling.”</li><li>“It feels so light and refreshing, but makes my skin feel clean and refreshed.”</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "quote_jzqpe6"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": true,
        "heading": "Content Requirements",
        "text": "<h2>Content Requirements</h2><p>Messaging must include:</p><ul><li>Light and calming spray, and doesn't leave skin sticky or tight.</li><li>Soothes redness and irritation without stinging or dryness.</li><li>Just mist and go — no rinsing, no mess.</li><li>Use after cleansing, post-workout, during travel, or anytime skin feels off.</li><li>100ml for everyday use, 15ml for on-the-go breakout control.</li><li>Gentle enough for sensitive or reactive skin.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
